Package: twweather
Type: Package
Title: Download Taiwan CWA Historical Weather Observations
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Liou", "Yuyou", email = "yuyou.liou@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A thin wrapper around the NCHU "CWB Historical Weather Data
    Downloader" (<https://mycolab.pp.nchu.edu.tw/historical_weather/>), which
    redistributes Central Weather Administration (CWA / CODiS) station
    observations. Provides three things: station metadata, station
    measurement time series (hourly / daily / monthly), and an
    aggregation of station data up to the township (鄉鎮) level by
    reverse-geocoding each station's longitude/latitude into township
    polygons (rainfall summed, other variables averaged).
